        <p><MadCap:variable name="Other.Product" /> supports authoring and output for left-to-right <MadCap:keyword term="Language support:LTR;LTR languages" />(LTR) as well as right-to-left <MadCap:keyword term="Language support:RTL;RTL languages" />(RTL) languages. This includes English, French, German, Japanese, Chinese, Arabic, Persian, Hebrew, multi-byte languages, and more. <MadCap:variable name="Other.Product" /> supports bi-directional languages not only at the topic level, but all the way down to the paragraph and sentence level.</p>
